comment: Faried (DEN) makes contact Young's (BKN) body, affecting his RSBQ at the start of his drive.
The ball is deflected out of bounds by BKN.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that DEN be awarded possession was upheld.
Brown (BKN) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect the freedom of movement of Faried (DEN) on the interior.
Larkin (BKN) makes contact that impedes Mudiay (DEN) at the start of his dribble.
Larkin (BKN) retreats legally as he defends Faried's (DEN) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the shot was taken before the clock reached 00:00 was upheld.
